  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Firepower Forge</strong> is a fast-paced multiplayer First Person shooter with highly customizable classes. Forge your class by selecting from a wide range of weapons, passive abilities and active abilities and deploy into battle! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2653720/extras/298d6007bca50620aae60b12ddfe2b9d.poster.avif?t=1772055431\" width=512 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2653720/extras/298d6007bca50620aae60b12ddfe2b9d.webm?t=1772055431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2653720/extras/298d6007bca50620aae60b12ddfe2b9d.mp4?t=1772055431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the environment to your advantage! some maps have features such as a controllable construction crane!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2653720/extras/e1ca262bc889c225fb4d11ea3c59a18d.poster.avif?t=1772055431\" width=640 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2653720/extras/e1ca262bc889c225fb4d11ea3c59a18d.webm?t=1772055431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2653720/extras/e1ca262bc889c225fb4d11ea3c59a18d.mp4?t=1772055431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has multiple exciting gamemodes such as Deathmatch, Battle Royale, King of The Hill and more!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Firepower Forge</strong> is a fast-paced multiplayer First Person shooter with highly customizable classes. Forge your class by selecting from a wide range of weapons, passive abilities and active abilities and deploy into battle! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2653720/extras/298d6007bca50620aae60b12ddfe2b9d.poster.avif?t=1772055431\" width=512 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2653720/extras/298d6007bca50620aae60b12ddfe2b9d.webm?t=1772055431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2653720/extras/298d6007bca50620aae60b12ddfe2b9d.mp4?t=1772055431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the environment to your advantage! some maps have features such as a controllable construction crane!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2653720/extras/e1ca262bc889c225fb4d11ea3c59a18d.poster.avif?t=1772055431\" width=640 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2653720/extras/e1ca262bc889c225fb4d11ea3c59a18d.webm?t=1772055431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2653720/extras/e1ca262bc889c225fb4d11ea3c59a18d.mp4?t=1772055431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has multiple exciting gamemodes such as Deathmatch, Battle Royale, King of The Hill and more!</p>",
